OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 15 MAR
OL,4,CBROADCAST STUDIOS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2013FGavin Grey presents the final
OL,7,Fnews programme to be broadcast from
OL,8,FStudio N8 at BBC Television Centre.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThe broadcast ended at 10.16pm.
OL,11,
OL,12,FThe studio was built for BBC News 24,
OL,13,Fwhich moved there in 1999. It was later
OL,14,Fhanded to BBC World News, which moved
OL,15,Fto New Broadcasting House in January
OL,16,F2013.
